<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Integrating Google Gemini to Node JS Application</title>
  <link href="./styles.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    * {
    box-sizing: border-box;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
}

body {
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    background-color: #f4f7fc;
    padding: 20px;
}

.container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    background-color: white;
    padding: 20px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
}

/* Header Section */
.header {
    border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
    padding-bottom: 15px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
}

.header h1 {
    font-size: 24px;
    font-weight: bold;
}

.header p {
    color: #666;
    font-size: 14px;
}

/* Endpoint Section */
.endpoint {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
}

.get-btn {
    background-color: #007bff;
    color: white;
    padding: 10px 15px;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-weight: bold;
    cursor: pointer;
    margin-right: 10px;
}

.endpoint-input {
    flex-grow: 1;
    padding: 10px;
    border: 1px solid #ddd;
    border-radius: 4px;
    margin-right: 10px;
}

.description {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: #666;
}

/* Information Section */
.info {
    background-color: #eef3f7;
    padding: 10px;
    border-radius: 5px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
}

.info p {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: #666;
}

/* Parameters Section */
.parameters-section h3 {
    font-size: 18px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
}

.parameters {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
}

.parameter {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
}

.parameter label {
    font-weight: bold;
    margin-bottom: 5px;
}

.parameter input {
    padding: 10px;
    border: 1px solid #ddd;
    border-radius: 4px;
}

.try-btn {
    background-color: #28a745;
    color: white;
    padding: 10px 20px;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-weight: bold;
    cursor: pointer;
}

.try-btn:hover {
    background-color: #218838;
}

/* Responses Section */
.responses-section h3 {
    font-size: 18px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
}

.response {
    background-color: #f7f9fc;
    padding: 20px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
}

.response-body {
    background-color: #ffffff;
    padding: 10px;
    border-radius: 5px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    border: 1px solid #ddd;
}

textarea.response-example {
    width: 100%;
    height: 200px;
    font-family: monospace;
    padding: 10px;
    border: 1px solid #ddd;
    border-radius: 5px;
    resize: none;
}

/* Headers Section */
.headers {
    margin-top: 20px;
}

.headers table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
}

.headers th, .headers td {
    border: 1px solid #ddd;
    padding: 10px;
    text-align: left;
}

.headers th {
    background-color: #f0f0f0;
}

.headers td {
    font-size: 14px;
}

  </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <!-- Header Section -->
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Integrating Google Gemini to Node JS Application</h1>
            
        </div>

        <!-- GET Endpoint Section -->
        <div class="endpoint">
            <button class="get-btn">GET</button>
            <input type="text" class="endpoint-input" value="/api/prompt">
            <span class="description">Get information based on prompt</span>
        </div>

        <!-- API Information Section -->
        <div class="info">
            <p>The API endpoint allows you to retrieve information based on your prompt. When accessing this endpoint, you will receive a response containing information based on the question you entered in the prompt.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Parameters Section -->
        <div class="parameters-section">
            <h3>Body</h3>
            <div class="parameters">
                <div class="parameter">
                <textarea rows="5" cols="30">
                    {
                        "prompt":"What is the value of pi?"
                    }
                </textarea>
                </div>
            
            </div>
    
        </div>

        <!-- Responses Section -->
        <div class="responses-section">
            <h3>Responses</h3>
            <div class="response">
                <h4>Status : 200 OK</h4><br>
                <div class="response-body">
                    <label for="media-type">Media type</label>
                    <select id="media-type">
                        <option value="application/json">application/json</option>
                    </select><br><br>
                    <textarea class="response-example">
                        {
                            "Result ": "The value of pi (π) is approximately **3.14159**. \n\nHowever, pi is an irrational number, meaning it cannot be expressed as a simple fraction. Its decimal representation goes on forever without repeating.  \n\nHere are some ways to express pi:\n\n* **Approximate value:** 3.14159\n* **Symbol:** π\n* **Fraction (approximate):** 22/7 (this is a common approximation, but not exact) \n\nIt's important to note that while we use approximations of pi for calculations, its true value is infinite and non-repeating. \n"
                        }
                    </textarea>
                    <br><br>
                    <img src="postman-gemini.png" width="1030px"/>
                </div>
            </div>
          
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
